OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F463A1773781557
OL,3,C'Not fit for purpose': Doctor says
OL,4,Chospital's condition is impacting care
OL,6,FA leading consultant at Wales' biggest
OL,7,Fhospital has said the current building
OL,8,Fis "not fit for purpose" and that
OL,9,Fstaff are "fighting the
OL,10,Finfrastructure" to provide quality
OL,11,Fcare for patients.
OL,13,FProfessor Argiris Asderakis is a
OL,14,Ftransplant consultant who has worked
OL,15,Fat the University Hospital of Wales in
OL,16,FCardiff for 25 years. He is highly
OL,17,Fskilled and treats some of Wales'
OL,18,Fsickest patients.
OL,1,Wj5hw}j5 ~shws                   G1/22
OL,2,W+.-'*%/"-$+,(,'T(,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,
OL,23,TppppppppppppppppppGsource: itv.com/news
OL,24,ANext Page BWales News CReg TV FThis Day
FL,464,460,260,120,000,100
PN,46302
SC,0002
CT,2,C
PS,c008
OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F463A1773781557
OL,3,C'Not fit for purpose': Doctor says
OL,4,Chospital's condition is impacting care
OL,6,FNow, as chair of the British Medical
OL,7,FAssociation's local negotiating
OL,8,Fcommittee and a member of the Welsh
OL,9,Fconsultants committee, he is speaking
OL,10,Fout about a structure that he says "is
OL,11,Fnot made for modern hospitals".
OL,13,FHe describes seeing sewage leaks in
OL,14,Fvarious parts of the hospital more
OL,15,Fthan once in the last year, toilets
OL,16,Fout of order, lifts breaking down and
OL,17,Fair conditioning and ventilation
OL,18,Ffailing.
OL,1,Wj5hw}j5 ~shws                   G2/22
OL,2,W+.-'*%/"-$+,(,'T(,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,
OL,23,TppppppppppppppppppGsource: itv.com/news
OL,24,ANext Page BWales News CReg TV FThis Day
FL,464,460,260,120,000,100
PN,46303
SC,0003
CT,2,C
PS,c008
OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F463A1773781557
OL,3,C'Not fit for purpose': Doctor says
OL,4,Chospital's condition is impacting care
OL,6,FHe claimed these ventilation problems
OL,7,Fcaused theatres to be closed and
OL,8,Fforced operations to be delayed or
OL,9,Fcancelled. He said on one occasion a
OL,10,Fleak resulted in a vascular radiology
OL,11,Fsuit being shut down for three weeks.
OL,13,F"It's everyday problems, some of them
OL,14,Fmay seem trivial but some of them are
OL,15,Fmuch more serious," he said.
OL,17,F"This is a place where important
OL,18,Foperations are done like aneurysms,
OL,19,Fwhich are life threatening, where
OL,20,Fimportant diagnostic tests take place
OL,21,Fand these tests didn't happen.
OL,1,Wj5hw}j5 ~shws                   G3/22
OL,2,W+.-'*%/"-$+,(,'T(,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,
OL,23,TppppppppppppppppppGsource: itv.com/news
OL,24,ANext Page BWales News CReg TV FThis Day
FL,464,460,260,120,000,100
PN,46304
SC,0004
CT,2,C
PS,c008
OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F463A1773781557
OL,3,C'Not fit for purpose': Doctor says
OL,4,Chospital's condition is impacting care
OL,6,F"It's not about a floor that leaks,
OL,7,Fit's about how patients suffer.
OL,9,F"We had two days where three of the
OL,10,Ftheatres had ventilation problems.
OL,11,FThey were sorted out within the hour
OL,12,Fbecause our estates team work really
OL,13,Fhard but that was an hour lost of
OL,14,Ftheatres - for three days, for two or
OL,15,Fthree different theatres.
OL,17,F"That means nine hours of work, a full
OL,18,Fday work for one theatre. Some
OL,19,Fpatients were postponed that day as a
OL,20,Fresult of that.
OL,1,Wj5hw}j5 ~shws                   G4/22
OL,2,W+.-'*%/"-$+,(,'T(,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,
OL,23,TppppppppppppppppppGsource: itv.com/news
OL,24,ANext Page BWales News CReg TV FThis Day
FL,464,460,260,120,000,100
PN,46305
SC,0005
CT,2,C
PS,c008
OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F463A1773781557
OL,3,C'Not fit for purpose': Doctor says
OL,4,Chospital's condition is impacting care
OL,6,F"Nurses had to stay late that day so
OL,7,Fcouldn't be on shift the next day.
OL,8,FThat has a knock on effect. You need a
OL,9,Fwell working system for a modern
OL,10,Fhospital to work and this is not
OL,11,Fconducive to that.
OL,13,F"We all try to mitigate for those
OL,14,Fcircumstances. Our estates team are
OL,15,Fbrilliant they try and do things -
OL,16,Fthey provide miracles there - with an
OL,17,Finfrastructure which is not fit for
OL,18,Fpurpose for the 20th century not to
OL,19,Fmention the 21st century."
OL,1,Wj5hw}j5 ~shws                   G5/22
OL,2,W+.-'*%/"-$+,(,'T(,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,
OL,23,TppppppppppppppppppGsource: itv.com/news
OL,24,ANext Page BWales News CReg TV FThis Day
FL,464,460,260,120,000,100
PN,46306
SC,0006
CT,2,C
PS,c008
OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F463A1773781557
OL,3,C'Not fit for purpose': Doctor says
OL,4,Chospital's condition is impacting care
OL,6,FFigures published by NHS Wales Shared
OL,7,FServices Partnership show that for the
OL,8,Fyear 2024 - 2025 it would cost over
OL,9,F#1.04bn to fix the backlog maintenance
OL,10,Fcosts across Wales' NHS estate.
OL,12,FOf this, over two thirds of
OL,13,Fmaintenance issues are considered
OL,14,F"high" or "significant" risks.
OL,1,Wj5hw}j5 ~shws                   G6/22
OL,2,W+.-'*%/"-$+,(,'T(,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,
OL,23,TppppppppppppppppppGsource: itv.com/news
OL,24,ANext Page BWales News CReg TV FThis Day
FL,464,460,260,120,000,100
PN,46307
SC,0007
CT,2,C
PS,c008
OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F463A1773781557
OL,3,C'Not fit for purpose': Doctor says
OL,4,Chospital's condition is impacting care
OL,6,FThe University Hospital of Wales (UHW)
OL,7,Ffalls within Cardiff and Vale health
OL,8,Fboard. The cost of fixing growing
OL,9,Fmaintenance problems across the health
OL,10,Fboard is estimated at more than #111m.
OL,11,FOver #41m of these are considered high
OL,12,Frisk maintenance issues.
OL,14,FConstruction of UHW started in 1966
OL,15,Fbefore being opened in 1971. While
OL,16,Fsome parts of the current hospital
OL,17,Fhave been updated since then, a vast
OL,18,Fmajority of the main building still
OL,19,Fdates back over five decades.
OL,1,Wj5hw}j5 ~shws                   G7/22
OL,2,W+.-'*%/"-$+,(,'T(,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,
OL,23,TppppppppppppppppppGsource: itv.com/news
OL,24,ANext Page BWales News CReg TV FThis Day
FL,464,460,260,120,000,100
PN,46308
SC,0008
CT,2,C
PS,c008
OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F463A1773781557
OL,3,C'Not fit for purpose': Doctor says
OL,4,Chospital's condition is impacting care
OL,6,FThere has been talk of replacing the
OL,7,Fhospital since before the pandemic and
OL,8,Fhealth board bosses have previously
OL,9,Fsaid the site is "no longer fit for
OL,10,Fpurpose".
OL,1,Wj5hw}j5 ~shws                   G8/22
OL,2,W+.-'*%/"-$+,(,'T(,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,
OL,23,TppppppppppppppppppGsource: itv.com/news
OL,24,ANext Page BWales News CReg TV FThis Day
FL,464,460,260,120,000,100
PN,46309
SC,0009
CT,2,C
PS,c008
OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F463A1773781557
OL,3,C'Not fit for purpose': Doctor says
OL,4,Chospital's condition is impacting care
OL,6,FAs part of their infrastructure plan
OL,7,Fin 2022-23 their report stated: "The
OL,8,Ftimely replacement of UHW is
OL,9,Fabsolutely critical to support our
OL,10,Flong-term strategy - the existing
OL,11,Finfrastructure is failing and much of
OL,12,Fthe current hospital accommodation and
OL,13,Fdepartments are no longer fit for
OL,14,Fpurpose in terms of functional layout,
OL,15,Fenvironmental suitability or physical
OL,16,Fcondition.
OL,26,@oD@aOU
OL,1,Wj5hw}j5 ~shws                   G9/22
OL,2,W+.-'*%/"-$+,(,'T(,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,
OL,23,TppppppppppppppppppGsource: itv.com/news
OL,24,ANext Page BWales News CReg TV FThis Day
FL,464,460,260,120,000,100
PN,46310
SC,0010
CT,2,C
PS,c008
OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F463A1773781557
OL,3,C'Not fit for purpose': Doctor says
OL,4,Chospital's condition is impacting care
OL,6,F"This results in poor patient
OL,7,Fexperience, demotivated workforce and
OL,8,Finefficiency in terms of service
OL,9,Fdelivery, facilities costs and
OL,10,Fmaintenance overheads."
OL,12,FBut while Labour have pledged to
OL,13,Frebuild the hospital if they win the
OL,14,FSenedd Election in May, the Welsh
OL,15,FGovernment have confirmed plans are in
OL,16,Ftheir infancy.
OL,18,FProfessor Asderakis said the structure
OL,19,Fis "at the end of its life cycle" and
OL,20,Fthat a new hospital is badly needed.
OL,1,Wj5hw}j5 ~shws                  G10/22
OL,2,W+.-'*%/"-$+,(,'T(,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,
OL,23,TppppppppppppppppppGsource: itv.com/news
OL,24,ANext Page BWales News CReg TV FThis Day
FL,464,460,260,120,000,100
PN,46311
SC,0011
CT,2,C
PS,c008
OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F463A1773781557
OL,3,C'Not fit for purpose': Doctor says
OL,4,Chospital's condition is impacting care
OL,6,FHe added: "It's an alien structure,
OL,7,Fit's a strange structure, it's
OL,8,Fsomething that used to be called the
OL,9,Fnuclear structure which means it is
OL,10,Fsomething that is not made for modern
OL,11,Fhospitals. You cannot modify it. You
OL,12,Fcannot expand it easily and the
OL,13,Fassumption it was built on is well,
OL,14,Fwell outdated now.
OL,16,F"The core building is beyond
OL,17,Fmaintenance now. We need to have the
OL,18,Finfrastructure to do our job and give
OL,19,Fthe best for our patients."
OL,1,Wj5hw}j5 ~shws                  G11/22
OL,2,W+.-'*%/"-$+,(,'T(,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,
OL,23,TppppppppppppppppppGsource: itv.com/news
OL,24,ANext Page BWales News CReg TV FThis Day
FL,464,460,260,120,000,100
PN,46312
SC,0012
CT,2,C
PS,c008
OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F463A1773781557
OL,3,C'Not fit for purpose': Doctor says
OL,4,Chospital's condition is impacting care
OL,6,FHe said that repairing the maintenance
OL,7,Fissues at the hospital is also
OL,8,Fessential in keeping medical staff
OL,9,Fworking in Wales.
OL,11,F"They (patients) see a small part of
OL,12,Fthe picture, we see the whole picture
OL,13,Fand it is quite demoralising," he said.
OL,15,F"It's particularly demoralising for
OL,16,Fyounger doctors who think that this is
OL,17,Fnormal, and it is not.
OL,19,F"We can see more and more colleagues
OL,20,Fleaving Wales, leaving the UK, because
OL,21,Fof infrastructure.
OL,26,@sD@GpmsD@Ppn
OL,1,Wj5hw}j5 ~shws                  G12/22
OL,2,W+.-'*%/"-$+,(,'T(,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,
OL,23,TppppppppppppppppppGsource: itv.com/news
OL,24,ANext Page BWales News CReg TV FThis Day
FL,464,460,260,120,000,100
PN,46313
SC,0013
CT,2,C
PS,c008
OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F463A1773781557
OL,3,C'Not fit for purpose': Doctor says
OL,4,Chospital's condition is impacting care
OL,6,F"It's not only about salaries, the
OL,7,Fthings you hear in the news, you are
OL,8,Fput off if you work in a hospital that
OL,9,Fis not fit for purpose.
OL,11,F"If you cannot park, if you cannot do
OL,12,Fyour work properly with modern IT
OL,13,Fequipment, if you cannot operate with
OL,14,Fmodern lights, you say what exactly is
OL,15,Fthe purpose - am I going to perform my
OL,16,Fbest here?
OL,18,F"It's an addressable situation if we
OL,19,Fplan for it. We all know money is
OL,20,Ftight but a plan is required.
OL,1,Wj5hw}j5 ~shws                  G13/22
OL,2,W+.-'*%/"-$+,(,'T(,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,
OL,23,TppppppppppppppppppGsource: itv.com/news
OL,24,ANext Page BWales News CReg TV FThis Day
FL,464,460,260,120,000,100
PN,46314
SC,0014
CT,2,C
PS,c008
OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F463A1773781557
OL,3,C'Not fit for purpose': Doctor says
OL,4,Chospital's condition is impacting care
OL,6,F"Every five years you delay the build
OL,7,Fof a new hospital it costs you
OL,8,Fprobably twice as much."
OL,10,FThe Welsh Government said that it is
OL,11,Finvesting millions of pounds this year
OL,12,Fto "modernise and safeguard" the NHS
OL,13,Festate and that "early planning is
OL,14,Funderway for the replacement of
OL,15,FUniversity Hospital of Wales".
OL,1,Wj5hw}j5 ~shws                  G14/22
OL,2,W+.-'*%/"-$+,(,'T(,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,
OL,23,TppppppppppppppppppGsource: itv.com/news
OL,24,ANext Page BWales News CReg TV FThis Day
FL,464,460,260,120,000,100
PN,46315
SC,0015
CT,2,C
PS,c008
OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F463A1773781557
OL,3,C'Not fit for purpose': Doctor says
OL,4,Chospital's condition is impacting care
OL,6,FIn a full statement they said: "The
OL,7,FWelsh Government is investing over
OL,8,F#500 million this year to modernise
OL,9,Fand safeguard the NHS estate. This
OL,10,Finvestment includes upgrading critical
OL,11,Finfrastructure, replacing essential
OL,12,Fequipment, enhancing digital systems
OL,13,Fto support new ways of working, and
OL,14,Fbacking major regional diagnostic and
OL,15,Fsurgical hubs. Our commitment is
OL,16,Fclear: safe, modern, digitallyenabled
OL,17,Ffacilities for patients and staff
OL,18,Facross Wales.
OL,1,Wj5hw}j5 ~shws                  G15/22
OL,2,W+.-'*%/"-$+,(,'T(,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,
OL,23,TppppppppppppppppppGsource: itv.com/news
OL,24,ANext Page BWales News CReg TV FThis Day
FL,464,460,260,120,000,100
PN,46316
SC,0016
CT,2,C
PS,c008
OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F463A1773781557
OL,3,C'Not fit for purpose': Doctor says
OL,4,Chospital's condition is impacting care
OL,6,F"Welsh Government is making
OL,7,Fsignificant, targeted investments to
OL,8,Fmodernise and safeguard the NHS estate
OL,9,Facross Wales.
OL,11,F"Over #500 million has been allocated
OL,12,Fthis year to improve hospital
OL,13,Fbuildings, replace essential
OL,14,Fequipment, modernise digital
OL,15,Finfrastructure, and support service
OL,16,Ftransformation. This includes circa
OL,17,F#100m in 2025-26 in discretionary
OL,18,Fcapital, plus #40 million of focused
OL,19,Finvestment to strengthen critical
OL,20,Finfrastructure, infection prevention,
OL,21,Fand fire safety.
OL,1,Wj5hw}j5 ~shws                  G16/22
OL,2,W+.-'*%/"-$+,(,'T(,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,
OL,23,TppppppppppppppppppGsource: itv.com/news
OL,24,ANext Page BWales News CReg TV FThis Day
FL,464,460,260,120,000,100
PN,46317
SC,0017
CT,2,C
PS,c008
OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F463A1773781557
OL,3,C'Not fit for purpose': Doctor says
OL,4,Chospital's condition is impacting care
OL,6,F"To improve access and reduce waiting
OL,7,Ftimes, Welsh Government is also
OL,8,Fbacking major regional centres of
OL,9,Fexcellence. The #29 million North
OL,10,FWales Surgical Centre will open
OL,11,Fshortly, and construction is underway
OL,12,Fon the over #100 million Llantrisant
OL,13,FHealth Park Phase 1 - a new regional
OL,14,Fdiagnostic hub.
OL,1,Wj5hw}j5 ~shws                  G17/22
OL,2,W+.-'*%/"-$+,(,'T(,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,
OL,23,TppppppppppppppppppGsource: itv.com/news
OL,24,ANext Page BWales News CReg TV FThis Day
FL,464,460,260,120,000,100
PN,46318
SC,0018
CT,2,C
PS,c008
OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F463A1773781557
OL,3,C'Not fit for purpose': Doctor says
OL,4,Chospital's condition is impacting care
OL,6,F"It is recognised that several
OL,7,Fhospitals will require substantial
OL,8,Fredevelopment or full replacement in
OL,9,Fthe coming years. Early planning is
OL,10,Funderway for the replacement of
OL,11,FUniversity Hospital of Wales, a new
OL,12,Fhospital for West Wales, and
OL,13,Fredevelopment work at Wrexham Maelor
OL,14,FHospital. These major schemes will be
OL,15,Ffor the next Government to take
OL,16,Fforward and will require additional
OL,17,Fsources of capital beyond the current
OL,18,Fprogramme.
OL,1,Wj5hw}j5 ~shws                  G18/22
OL,2,W+.-'*%/"-$+,(,'T(,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,
OL,23,TppppppppppppppppppGsource: itv.com/news
OL,24,ANext Page BWales News CReg TV FThis Day
FL,464,460,260,120,000,100
PN,46319
SC,0019
CT,2,C
PS,c008
OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F463A1773781557
OL,3,C'Not fit for purpose': Doctor says
OL,4,Chospital's condition is impacting care
OL,6,F"This investment reflects Welsh
OL,7,FGovernment's commitment to ensuring
OL,8,Fsafe, modern, highquality NHS
OL,9,Ffacilities for patients and staff
OL,10,Facross Wales."
OL,12,FAddressing the maintenance backlog
OL,13,Fwith the health board itself, a
OL,14,Fspokesperson for Cardiff and Vale
OL,15,FUniversity Health Board said: "We
OL,16,Frecognise the challenges associated
OL,17,Fwith delivering care in older
OL,18,Fhealthcare environments, particularly
OL,19,Fat the University Hospital of Wales,
OL,20,Fand take the condition of the estate
OL,21,Fextremely seriously.
OL,26,@wD@_OU
OL,1,Wj5hw}j5 ~shws                  G19/22
OL,2,W+.-'*%/"-$+,(,'T(,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,
