OL,24,ANext Page BWales News CReg TV FThis Day
FL,464,460,260,120,000,100
PN,46320
SC,0020
CT,2,C
PS,c008
OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F463A1773781557
OL,3,C'Not fit for purpose': Doctor says
OL,4,Chospital's condition is impacting care
OL,6,F"Patient and colleague safety remains
OL,7,Fcentral to all activity. Services
OL,8,Fcontinue to operate with established
OL,9,Fand robust arrangements to manage and
OL,10,Fmonitor risk, while acknowledging the
OL,11,Fexperience of those delivering and
OL,12,Freceiving care within facilities that
OL,13,Fpresent complex and long-standing
OL,14,Fchallenges.
OL,1,Wj5hw}j5 ~shws                  G20/22
OL,2,W+.-'*%/"-$+,(,'T(,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,
OL,23,TppppppppppppppppppGsource: itv.com/news
OL,24,ANext Page BWales News CReg TV FThis Day
FL,464,460,260,120,000,100
PN,46321
SC,0021
CT,2,C
PS,c008
OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F463A1773781557
OL,3,C'Not fit for purpose': Doctor says
OL,4,Chospital's condition is impacting care
OL,6,F"The Health Board is taking a
OL,7,Fstructured and proactive approach to
OL,8,Fmaintaining and improving the estate,
OL,9,Fwith clear oversight of priorities and
OL,10,Ffocus on areas of greatest need. This
OL,11,Fincludes actions to support safe and
OL,12,Feffective care alongside longer-term
OL,13,Fplanning to ensure facilities are
OL,14,Fresilient and fit for the future.
OL,1,Wj5hw}j5 ~shws                  G21/22
OL,2,W+.-'*%/"-$+,(,'T(,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,
