FL,464,460,260,120,000,100
PN,46322
SC,0022
CT,2,C
PS,c008
OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F463A1773781557
OL,3,C'Not fit for purpose': Doctor says
OL,4,Chospital's condition is impacting care
OL,6,F"Work is continuing in close
OL,7,Fpartnership with Welsh Government to
OL,8,Fsupport ongoing improvement and
OL,9,Finvestment, alongside a continued
